| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3263 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dbcdae35-37ec-5504-8945-21d128fa96a2"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
